# Open Lens DB

An open source website and database for camera lens models.

# Developing

```sh
docker compose -f docker-compose-dev.yml build
```

```sh
docker compose -f docker-compose-dev.yml up
```

# Troubleshooting

If you get an error like: `vite: command not found` in the frontend container, you need to run:

```sh
cd frontend/openlensdb
npm install
```
